  8вҶ’Implement loop_runner.rs вҖ” the top-level orchestrator that drives the autoresearch experiment loop by iterating over specialists, running experiments via run_single_experiment (T11), tracking budget (T10), logging results (T12), managing git state (T14), and handling keep/discard decisions with consecutive failure counting.
