  3вҶ’//! The SwarmExecutor is the bridge between Forge and Claude Code swarms. It:
  4вҶ’//! - Starts a CallbackServer to receive progress updates
  5вҶ’//! - Builds the orchestration prompt using the SwarmContext
  6вҶ’//! - Spawns a Claude Code process with the prompt
