Also note: `RunStatus` and `TaskStatus` conversions are deferred вҖ” domain `TaskStatus` has data-carrying variants (`Running { agent_id, since }`, `Completed { result, duration }`, etc.) that require manual conversion, not the macro. These are needed when implementing the daemon (Plan 2), not for the foundation layer.

